title: S14 Ep91: The Supernatural Side of Sasquatch
itunes:title: The Supernatural Side of Sasquatch
description:
Tobe Johnson is a Bigfoot hunter and UFO experiencer from Oregon. Tobe's experiences have always been on the supernatural side, but at the same time, he tackles them from a very logical and believable perspective. BEYOND the DARKNESS sits down with Tobe today to discuss these fantastic experiences and plays audio from them as well! Plus, we discuss Tobe's own unique podcast!

Tobe's Website: http://www.strangebrau.com/
